{"tid":1956514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"狗 : 派紙口罩因曾有羈留人士利用口罩內的鐵線作自殘 昨日已改派CSI口罩","createTime":"2020-04-03T08:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T09:25:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f09bf3746c1201fc254a6c1adea10b3a69ba98c","tid":1956514,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:32:30.000Z","msg":"警方昨日起向羈留人士提供CSI口罩<br />\n03.04.2020 16:28<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，因應疫情發展及平衡被羈留人士的個人安全，昨天起向被羈留人士提供由懲教署生產的CSI外科口罩。警方解釋，過往曾發生被羈留人士利用外科口罩內的鐵線作自殘行為，因此較早前曾提供一種兩層結構，沒有鐵線的口罩給被羈留人士使用。警方又強調，會盡力確保被羈留人士及有機會接觸人士的安全。<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺區議員林兆彬表示，星期三有被捕支援律師反映，被捕人士原本所配戴的口罩被警方檢取作證物，旺角警署及紅磡警署只向被捕人士提供紙口罩，口罩只有兩層如紙巾薄的物料，鼻樑位置亦沒有金屬線 ，質疑不合防疫規格，對被捕人士和警員的健康構成威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278550&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1278550%26csid%3D261_341&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BgESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=def06710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1278550&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"8ec1dbb9e3040ac1dc0c33dca57eec84d805a556","tid":1956514,"uid":269061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:33:49.000Z","msg":"多謝林兆彬"},{"pid":"ad571d844c4d7a57c13ece8285986cff65d95caa","tid":1956514,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebab027fd00408e91cef9210bc9032221cc88996","tid":1956514,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T08:58:52.000Z","msg":"「解悶工廠」 點解還押抗爭者仲睇到連登？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"03a75d2fb0a9194c619c9bb4a6809882a850280d","tid":1956514,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:03:05.000Z","msg":"衣服都可以綁起上吊<br />\n<br />\n係咪要受捕人全裸？"},{"pid":"10acd1a450d2d7e6bc217df5c42d8135a0d88321","tid":1956514,"uid":74933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"口罩入面條鐵線點自殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪當人好似佢地班狗咁on9啦"}]}